I know it must look scary from the outside because in an emergency (like we saw two weeks ago with the china regulation) there are lots of people running for a very small exit door. Any serious bitcoin holders don't get too worried about the short term drops though, most of us hold because we believe you will all be running for a very small entrance door if the financial trouble hits (think 2008). We could be wrong, you could be wrong, but (especially if you have a lot of wealth) you may want to consider placing bets on both sides of the table for this one.</description>                            
